    "[90], a structured support vector machine (SVM) [116] is learned by maximizing a classification score, preventing labeling ambiguity in the training process.",
    "DatasetsWith the emergence of multi-modal tracking methods, several datasets and challenges for RGB-D and RGB-T tracking have been released.",
    "We summarize the available datasets in Table 2.",
    "Public dataset RGB-D datasetIn 2012, a small-scale dataset called BoBoT-D [48] was constructed, consisting of five RGB-D video sequences captured by the Kinect V1 sensor.",
    "Both overlap and hit rate are used for evaluation, to indicate the mean overlap between result and ground truth and percentage of frames with overlap larger than 0.33."
